{"tid":388863,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「童年遊戲」有無人有玩過勇者online","createTime":"2017-09-05T17:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T04:16:33.000Z","uid":141897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f91a46f751a50b7c1de93aa8f62f34b4ad85cbd0","tid":388863,"uid":141897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"可以用騎士卡變身（我記得有個叫電車騎士，攞把矛插人），再課多舊電池，型都癡線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲好記得最高階嘅武器係「入魔級」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而最型一定係槍手彈個銀仔上天，再射個銀仔反彈落返嚟招技。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好似浮游炮嘅三管壓縮。<br />\n<br />\n好多好多，但已經玩唔返啦，童年遊戲只能靠記憶回味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知仲有冇人記得呢隻game呢？"},{"pid":"d99aeea6fe90dbadba558471b9f952320b1e5c6b","tid":388863,"uid":141897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654ca7bb1f26998cb5e5a2edac532a502c53fe83","tid":388863,"uid":2071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"勇者online唔係榮耀前身咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8034636a285eb1cdaaa702b91bc7e219aedebd6","tid":388863,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勇者online唔係榮耀前身咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都記得係，<br />\n果陣係雲起代理，<br />\n仲要打電話有GM接聽嘅年代"},{"pid":"ef75759741c15e23d68ad32ff560555b1284db9b","tid":388863,"uid":84646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"竟然有人識依隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805122957cc273249f7856a71669b31c0d80a835","tid":388863,"uid":141897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot